summary: dude the fact that Dan does anything is so impressive to me sometimes?? Like I also have clinical depression and my motivation...
body: dude the fact that Dan does anything is so impressive to me sometimes?? Like I also have clinical depression and my motivation is at a 0 99% of the time and this motherfucker is out here taking care of himself? Exercising? Going on a world tour with his soulmate and meeting hundreds of fans and doing it all whilst also making content for instagram twitter and the gaming channel??? He does so much honestly I could never in a million years be salty about him not also making a dinof vid. I just don’t get it.
